prop.name: dateModified
prop.desc: The date on which the CreativeWork was most recently modified or when the item's entry was modified within a DataFeed.

prop.name: dateDeleted
prop.desc: The datetime the item was removed from the DataFeed.

prop.name: dateCreated
prop.desc: The date on which the CreativeWork was created or the item was added to a DataFeed.

prop.name: item
prop.desc: An entity represented by an entry in a list or data feed (e.g. an 'artist' in a list of 'artists')’.
